Muhammadans and Christians will see the vanity of their religious
doctrines.* Men fight about religion on earth -- in heaven they shall
find out that there is only one true religion -- the worship of God's
**S**PIRIT."\*

In other words -- "**T**HERE IS NO RELIGION (OR LAW) HIGHER THAN TRUTH"
-- "**SATYAT NASTI PARO DHARMAH**" -- the motto of the Maharajah of
Benares, adopted by the Theosophical Society.

